---
title: Veggie Fritter Burger with Slaw, Fries & Plant-Based Mayo
description: Welcome to a new world of veggie burgers. Instead of a patty, you’ll fry up a tasty fritter filled with grated veggies and
plant-based 'cheese', then pile it with slaw on a brioche bun. With a smear of plant-based mayo and potato fries on the side, this
is a burger for the record books!
